data.description: Back on Market!!. price lowered!  Country Club Ranches, Prime location proximal to 1-75 and Turnpike, Upscale  turnkey home sits on oversized 39, 447 lot and features a large pool with jacuzzi, covered drive thru, SECURITY electronic gate,  impact doors and double pane windows, wood Cabinetry & Granite counters, porcelain floors, 4 bedrooms 2 1/2 baths, Walk in closet in Master Bedroom, and HUGE great room housing family, kitchen and plenty of Eating spaces, 2 car Garage Tiled and air conditioned with Split AC. for ADDING STORAGE, lot is almost an ACRE, plenty of space for your Vehicles, Boat, RV. HAS 2 Horse stalls, and a brand NEW STORAGE SHED, property has 10 COCONUT TREES and many more TROPICAL FRUIT TREES on grounds.  House sits on a very spacious private lot, and NO HOA FEES
